dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Jackson County, WI 2015
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Jackson_Hydro_2015.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'JACKSON_HYDROLINE_2015' and 'JACKSON_HYDROPOLY_2015'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
